data.description: INCREDIBLE - This is the home that you absolutely must see ... This large, open, and bright 2 story home sits on a full daylight basement and nearly 6 ACRES of beautiful land. This property is surrounded by the 85-acre nature preserve and WSA property, plus an additional 50 acres of conservation land. So, your privacy will be protected here. Enjoy the wooded serenity, space for horses, and peaceful, babbling creek. Bring your horses, enjoy peaceful fire pits, your own private swimming hole, or any other outside activity in this personal oasis. The property sits at the very end of Punktintown Road, adjacent to the new nature preserve area being built by the county. This home and property is truly unique and special!
